data.description: Spectacular Golf course, lake & skyline views from this exclusive 2 BD, 2 BA tower suite on the 25th floor. This bright & airy home has many upgrades, volume ceilings 10ft., access to a large private balcony from every room. Kitchen granite countertops & backsplash, SS appliances & wood cabinets. Large custom-made pantry. Breakfast area. Formal dining room. Master bathroom updated with marble countertops. Walk-in closets. Tile floors throughout. Smooth ceilings & crown moldings. Hurricane Shutters. Luxury 5-star resort living: 2 pools, private gourmet restaurant & movie theatre, state of the art fitness center/spa, fitness classes included, tennis, racquetball, coffee shop, party rooms & kids’ room. 24hr valet & security. Close to shopping, restaurants & houses of worship. Great schools.
